<!-- END APPRAISAL FORM -->
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      I know Middle Park as part of the western corridor market I work closely. The buyer profile here is predominantly upsizers: people who have owned elsewhere in Brisbane's west, who have some equity behind them, and who want to land in a suburb with a specific residential character that the bigger, more developed addresses in the corridor cannot quite replicate. The small number of available homes relative to buyer demand means that when a well-presented property comes to market in Middle Park, genuine competition tends to follow.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      The housing stock is a mix of 1970s and 1980s brick homes, with some elevated properties on blocks that offer valley or partial views toward the Brisbane River corridor. Tree coverage is strong throughout, giving the suburb its leafy character. Kenmore is a short drive north, providing access to Kenmore Village and Kenmore State High School catchment, which is a draw for families with older children. Jindalee's retail strip and Sinnamon Park shopping cover the everyday needs. The Centenary Motorway is accessible within minutes, making the suburb practical for CBD commuters who value a quieter home base.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Western Corridor Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Low turnover, genuine scarcity</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Leafy Peaceful Streets</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Upsizer and family demand</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/jindalee" style="color:#b98229;">Jindalee</a>, <a href="/suburbs/riverhills" style="color:#b98229;">Riverhills</a>, <a href="/suburbs/kenmore" style="color:#b98229;">Kenmore</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===================================================
     SECTION: FAQ
